Map Name:  HW_CARTOONFIGHT_B1
Date Made: 11th June 2006
Map Author: Mammoth (Jamie Watson)

----------------------------------------------

Textures Author: Mammoth
Description: The textures didn't take long to make since they are rather simple.  They look good and I shall be developing more detailed textures.

-----------------------------------------------

This map took 2 days to make.  I think that this map is a good fun map to play.  I had great fun training a member of my clan on this map.  And had loads of good fun games playing this map.  It has camping spots and close combat action places.  There is also 2 ways to the outside of the map which i will leave you to find, believe me they are difficult.

------------------------------------------------

Finally this is a BETA map, i need to know of bugs, feedback and suggestions to improve this map.  In order for this I would like you to contact me either via MSN or via Email.  Thank you.

Have fun playing this map :D

MSN: mammoth@jamiew.info
Email: wako_hair_jay@hotmail.com
